Feature: Memory
  Background:
    Given the JSON is:
      """
      {
        "array": [

        ],
        "false": false,
        "float": 10.0,
        "hash": {
        },
        "integer": 10,
        "null": null,
        "string": "json_spec",
        "true": true
      }
      """
    And I get the JSON

  Scenario: Entire JSON
    When I keep the JSON as "JSON"
    Then the JSON should be %{JSON}
    And the JSON should be:
      """
      %{JSON}
      """

  Scenario: String
    When I keep the JSON at "string" as "STRING"
    Then the JSON at "string" should be %{STRING}
    And the JSON should be:
      """
      {
        "array": [

        ],
        "false": false,
        "float": 10.0,
