    And I keep the JSON at "true" as "TRUE"
    And I keep the JSON at "false" as "FALSE"
    And I keep the JSON at "null" as "NULL"
    Then the JSON should have the following:
      | string  | %{STRING}  |
      | integer | %{INTEGER} |
